{"tid":1729285,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大校委高票當選 促防警擅闖","createTime":"2019-11-17T07:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T07:26:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf734200464231784e341195ecfc0addf43c196b","tid":1729285,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T07:21:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191117/MN5TQZPEW4V4NWLVPXKBVAAKCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191117%2FMN5TQZPEW4V4NWLVPXKBVAAKCQ%2F&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ6HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=e1bbca85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191117%2FMN5TQZPEW4V4NWLVPXKBVAAKCQ%2F&h=f766e42b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191117/MN5TQZPEW4V4NWLVPXKBVAAKCQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n港大校委高票當選 促防警擅闖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191117/large/1573921304_9603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191117%2Flarge%2F1573921304_9603.jpg&h=f02c60b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李梓成<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港大學校委會本科生代表選舉結果昨日公佈，李梓成以4,450票當選，另一候選人麥嘉晉則以121票落敗，另有40票棄權及18票廢票。李已於昨日正式成為校委會本科生代表，任期為一年。<br />\n<br />\n李梓成其後在個人社交媒體上發文感謝同學信任，在任期內會堅持向校長提出訴求，包括任何學生不得因參與政治運動被判刑而被剝奪學籍、痛斥大學管治架構對學生發出的任何不當言論、大學領導層須以對話解決分歧及防止警察闖入校園，竭力守護大學。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n畢業典禮取消<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：稱行動毋須上報 官媒速刪報道<br />\n<br />\n對上一次校委會本科生代表網上投票在4月舉行，前署理學生會會長黃程鋒以189票當選，另一候選人麥嘉晉則以55票落敗。今次網上投票總票數為4,611票，投票人數比以往高出18倍，港大學生會媒體《學苑》認為，結果反映同學在社會運動下，公民意識得到增長。今次選舉是由於黃程鋒在8月30日遇襲，離開香港。<br />\n<br />\n另外，港大校方表示，鑑於持續不明朗的狀況以及交通服務受阻，決定取消學院原定於本月底至12月舉行的畢業典禮。大學將通知畢業生領取畢業證書，會因情況決定是否於本學年度另訂時間為畢業生舉行慶祝會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191117/large/1573921303_a692.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191117%2Flarge%2F1573921303_a692.jpg&h=2f2bec4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港大校方取消學院原定於月底至12月舉行的畢業典禮。資料圖片<br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"db121fb57925e045f878e6a72122e967010e1445","tid":1729285,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"警察砲轟poly，要推畀國際知！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter 組不斷更新 Task3</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ6HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=20436135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">/task3</span></span>就得！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有一定要響外國議員/名人/外媒關於香港的tweets reply Poly最新情況，向國際求救</span><br />\n<br />\n！！！眾志：解放軍拎自動步槍同刺刀<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1195948090118721536?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1195948090118721536%3Fs%3D19&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ6HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=33c62303\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1195948090118721536%3Fs%3D19&h=c655ebea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1195948090118721536?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n！！用音波炮對付示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/antd/status/1195954714380132352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fantd%2Fstatus%2F1195954714380132352&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ6HX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=7cfc6466\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fantd%2Fstatus%2F1195954714380132352&h=05c4ea5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/antd/status/11959547